			<div>

	<pb n="0001" facs="liv_001007_0001"/><!--pb/@n='01'--> 
<!--hand 01 top left Livingstone--><!--Stamp University College London, Galton Papers, 190-->
<lb/><p rend="center"><space extent="3" unit="chars"/><placeName>57 Sloane St</placeName></p>
<lb/><p rend="center"><space extent="1" unit="words"/><space extent="1" unit="chars"/>25<hi rend="sup underline">th</hi> April</p>
<lb/><p rend="center"><space extent="1" unit="words"/><space extent="3" unit="chars"/>1857</p>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent">My Dear <persName>M<hi rend="sup underline">r</hi> Galton</persName></p>
<lb/><p><space extent="2" unit="chars"/>I am sorry that 
<lb/>my engagments during 
<lb/>the whole of next 
<lb/>week will prevent 
<lb/>my having the pleasure 
<lb/>of accepting your 
<lb/>kind invitation to 
<lb/>dinner on thursday 

	<pb n="0002" facs="liv_001007_0002"/><!--pb/@n='02'--> 
<lb/>I regret this as 
<lb/>it would give me 
<lb/>much pleasure 
<lb/>to have a little talk 
<lb/>with you </p>
<lb/><p><space extent="1" unit="chars"/>I am &amp; </p>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent"><space extent="2" unit="chars"/><persName>D. Livingstone</persName></p>
			
</div>
